achievement.title: Webbing Crashers
achievement.description: Defeat Elerethe Renferal in The Emerald Nightmare after destroying all her Pulsing Egg Sacs during the encounter on Normal difficulty or higher.

achievement.title: Imagined Dragons World Tour
achievement.description: Defeat Ysondre in The Emerald Nightmare while all members of the raid have Dream Essences from all four gateway locations on Normal difficulty or higher.

achievement.title: Buggy Fight
achievement.description: Defeat Nythendra in The Emerald Nightmare after squishing 15 Glow Bugs on Normal difficulty or higher.
